latestPosts.caption:
I’ve always been mesmerised by the intricacies of the miniature paintings, how every fine line and jewel - tone hues tell centuries of royal stories. 

This image is inspired by the miniature painting of a young woman taking a bath and styling her hair. I’m both a student and story - teller, learning, dreaming and creating visuals that are rooted in heritage for @thepalaceatelier ♥️
